---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import GetQuoete from "../../../components/buttons/GetQuote.astro";
import Testimonials from "../../../components/Testimonials";
import ButtonScrollTop from "../../../components/buttons/ButtonScrollTop";
---

<link
  rel="canonical"
  href="https://cayadservices.com/for-individuals/enclosed-auto-transport"
/>
<style>
  .custom-background {
    background:
      linear-gradient(hsla(250, 75%, 5%, 0.5), rgba(6, 3, 21, 0.5)),
      url("/img/enclosed-car.webp") center center no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }
</style>

<Layout
  title="Enclosed Car Transport | Cayad Auto Transport"
  content="Cost effective enclosed car transport 10.000+ shippings, ensuring the highest level of safety and protection for your vehicle during transit. 5 stars call now !"
>
  <div
    class="container-fluid flex flex-col items-center justify-center custom-background h-[60vh]"
  >
    <div class="w-[80%]">
      <p
        class="text-white text-[4rem] xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] font-bold"
        data-aos="fade-down"
      >
        Enclosed Car Transport
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold">
        Cayad is the most cost effective enclosed car shipping solution in the U.S
      </h1>
      <GetQuoete />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 flex justify-center mb-8">
    <Testimonials title="Real Reviews on Enclosed Auto Transport Services" client:load />
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#00000] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          Enclosed Auto Shipping Services
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-8 text-black">
        Protect what matters most. With <strong>enclosed vehicle transportation</strong>, your luxury or classic car travels shielded from weather and road debris safe, secure, and handled with expert care.
        <br /><br />
        Need pricing? Our <strong>enclosed car transport quote</strong> tool gives you instant, transparent rates based on your route and vehicle type, no hidden <strong>car carrier cost</strong>, just premium protection from start to finish.
        <br /><br />
        Choose peace of mind. Choose <strong>Cayad</strong>.
      </p>
  
        
      </div>
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img
          src="/img/enclosed-car2.webp"
          class="rounded-xl"
          height={400}
          width={640}
          sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 50vw"
          alt="enclosed auto transport"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img
          src="/img/enclosed-car1.webp"
          width="1632"
          height="918"
          class="rounded-xl"
          alt="enclosed auto transport deportive vehicle"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#00000] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          How Much Does Enclosed Auto Transport Cost?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-8 text-black">
          Wondering <strong>how much do car haulers charge per mile</strong>? On average, <strong>enclosed car shipping rates</strong> are 30–40% higher than <a href="/for-individuals/open-car-transport/" class="text-btn-blue hover:underline">open transport</a> due to the added protection. Expect to pay around $709 for short routes, $929 for medium, and $1179+ for long-distance shipping. <br><br>At Cayad, we deliver the best value on your <strong>enclosed auto transport cost</strong>, combining security, care, and competitive pricing.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#00000] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          Do You Need Enclosed Car Transport? 
        </h2>
        <div
          class="lg:w-1/2 feature-text animate__animated animate__fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.1s"
        >
          <div
            class="flex mb-5 animate__animated animate__fadeInUp"
            data-wow-delay="0.3s"
          >
            <ol>
              <p class="mb-0 text-base text-black">
                Not sure if <strong>enclosed auto transport</strong> is the right fit? Consider these quick questions:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-4 text-black text-sm">
                <li>Do you consider your vehicle a valuable investment?</li>
                <li>Are you concerned about snow, cold weather, or road conditions?</li>
                <li>Is protecting your car from dust, dirt, or flying debris important to you?</li>
                <li>Does your vehicle have a custom finish or vintage paint job?</li>
                <li>Do you want extra protection against theft or vandalism?</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-4 text-black text-sm">
                If you answered yes to any of these, enclosed shipping through trusted <strong>automobile carriers</strong> is your best choice. 
                While the <strong>auto transport cost per mile</strong> may be slightly higher, the added security is worth every penny, especially for high-value or rare vehicles.
              </p>

            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img
          src="/img/enclosed-car3.webp"
          width="1000"
          height="750"
          class="rounded-xl"
          alt="enclosed car transport vehicle been pick up"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div>
      <h2
        class="font-semibold xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:px-4 sm:px-4 text-[2.5rem]"
      >
        Why You'll Love Choosing Enclosed Auto Transport
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:px-4 sm:px-4">
      <div
        class="grid mt-8 grid-cols-2 xs:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 w-full gap-6"
      >
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.3s"
        >
          <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-black font-bold">
            Premium Protection That Gives You Peace of Mind
          </h5>
          <p class="py-4">
            Shield your vehicle from rain, dust, and road debris with <strong>enclosed auto transport</strong>. It’s the choice trusted by <a href="/for-individuals/classic-cars-auto-transport/" class="text-btn-blue hover:underline">collectors and luxury</a> car owners for one reason, unmatched safety. A small upgrade, a huge relief.
          </p>

        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.5s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-black font-bold">
              Safeguarded from Rain and Hazards
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4">
              With <strong>enclosed auto transport</strong>, your vehicle stays protected from rain, snow, dust, and road hazards. It's the smart choice for preserving the shine and value of your <a href="/for-individuals/classic-cars-auto-transport/" class="text-btn-blue hover:underline">exotic or luxury</a> car, because it deserves more than just a ride.
            </p>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.7s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#00000] font-bold">
              Ideal for Low Ground Clearance Cars
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4">
              Have a sports car or custom build with low clearance? <strong>Enclosed auto transport</strong> is your safest option. Our <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tail_lift" class="text-btn-blue hover:underline">hydraulic lift gates</a> ensure smooth loading and unloading, no scrapes, no stress, just full protection from the ground up.
            </p>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.9s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 text-xl py-4 text-[#00000] font-bold">
              Transport Multiple Vehicles with Confidence
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4">
              Need to ship a fleet or multiple high-value cars? <strong>Cayad Auto Transport</strong> offers secure <strong>enclosed auto transport</strong> for one or several vehicles at once. Our network of trusted <strong>automobile carriers</strong> ensures top-tier service and rates, ideal for <a href="/for-individuals/classic-cars-auto-transport/" class="text-btn-blue hover:underline">collectors</a>, <a href="/for-businesses/auto-dealers/" class="text-btn-blue hover:underline">dealerships</a>, and families.
            </p>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="w-full flex mb-8 flex-col items-center xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-0 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-0 mx-auto overflow-hidden px-0"
  >
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-4 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-4 py-10 px-0"
    >
      <h2 class="text-4xl text-[#00000] font-medium mb-10">
        Enclosed Auto Transport Is the Smartest Choice for Protection
      </h2>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 xs:grid-cols-1 gap-10"
      >
        <div class="wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img
              src="/img/dollar.webp"
              width="1080"
              height="1080"
              class="w-24 h-20 mb-2"
              alt="enclosed car shipping dollar logo"
            />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-black">Experienced Classic Car Haulers</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0 text-black">
                Our expert <strong>classic car haulers</strong> know how to handle <strong>enclosed car shipping</strong> with care. At <strong>Cayad Auto Transport</strong>, we select top drivers to protect your <a href="/for-individuals/classic-cars-auto-transport/" class="text-btn-blue hover:underline">luxury</a> and  <a href="/for-individuals/classic-cars-auto-transport/" class="text-btn-blue hover:underline">vintage vehicles.</a>
              </p>


            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img
              src="/img/easy.webp"
              width="1080"
              height="1080"
              class="w-24 h-20 mb-2"
              alt="enclosed car shipping easy logo"
            />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-black">A+ Service</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0 text-black">
              Every <strong>antique car hauler</strong> meets strict insurance standards, offering premium peace of mind. For vehicles valued over $50,000, we strongly recommend <strong>enclosed auto transport</strong> the most secure way to manage the true <strong>cost to move a car cross country</strong>.
            </p>



            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
            <img
              src="/img/call.webp"
              width="120"
              height="120"
              class="w-24 h-24 mb-2"
              alt="enclosed car transport call logo"
            />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-black">
                Covered Auto Transport Compliance Standards
              </h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0 text-black">
                Our compliance <a href="/why-us/our-team/" class="text-btn-blue hover:underline">team</a> vets every exotic carrier to guarantee professional service. We ensure the best <strong>enclosed car transport cost per mile</strong> with trusted, high-standard haulers.
              </p>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-[95%] wow"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-delay="100"
          style="min-height: 400px;"
        >
          <div class="h-full">
            <img
              src="/img/enclosed.webp"
              width="1645"
              height="11234"
              class="object-cover rounded-xl w-full h-full"
              alt="enclosed car shipping delivery"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ButtonScrollTop client:load />
</Layout>
